<p>
<note n="0099001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0099001">曰＝言【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0100001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0100001">芽＝牙【宋】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0100002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0100002">想＝相【宮】</note>
